creator: SpareBank 1
descriptionHtml:
This application provides customized banking services for your business and provides easy access to your most frequently used banking services while "on the go". All the services are designed so you are able to carry out daily banking needs wherever you are. In addition to the quick balance feature and mobile banking, we have added some useful features that we hope you will enjoy.

In mobile banking, you can transfer funds between your own accounts, approve payments and get a complete overview of your accounts and funding. To log on to mobile banking, you can use the one-time password and "Password" (new), or BankID for Mobile. The password can be created on our website, under the menu option “Mobile”.
descriptionShort: Mobile banking gives you easy access to your banking services while on the go.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
New in 5.1.2:
- Improved performance and bugfixes.

Please let us know what you think about the app! We value your feedback :)

title: SpareBank 1 Mobilbank bedrift

creator: SpareBank 1
descriptionHtml:
The app offers banking services for your business needs on the go. If you want to get in touch with the bank, you can do so by starting a chat from the app.

You can transfer funds between your own accounts, pay bills using the invoice scanner and get a complete overview when you are on the move. The app notifies you about new payments for approval.

To log in for the first time, you will have to use BankID. The next time you can log in with biometrics like fingerprint or face recognition (if supported), or PIN.
descriptionShort: Mobile banking gives you easy access to your banking services while on the go.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
This version contains:
- Improved overview of accounts with loans, credit, and deposits.
- Bugfixes and other small improvements.
